column_definitions.name: Subject
column_definitions.comment: The zebrafish being studied at two timepoints.

column_definitions.name: Nucleic Region 1
column_definitions.comment: The nucleic region of Image 1 used for alignment.

column_definitions.name: Nucleic Region 2
column_definitions.comment: The nucleic region of Image 2 used for alignment.

column_definitions.name: Region 1 URL
column_definitions.comment: URL for CSV containing nucleic Region 1 segments in aligned micron coordinate grid.

column_definitions.name: Region 2 URL
column_definitions.comment: URL for CSV containing nucleic Region 2 segments in aligned micron coordinate grid.

column_definitions.name: Alignment
column_definitions.comment: Computed alignment transform for Image 2 into Image 1 coordinates.

column_definitions.name: Old Alignment
column_definitions.comment: The original iterative-closest-points alignment, now superceded by an optimized Alignment matrix.

column_definitions.name: Alignment ZYX Slice
column_definitions.comment: An axes-aligned ROI in image 1 voxel space used to compute an optimized Alignment. Format: z0:z1,y0:y1,x0:x1
